## 11. Core Data Models (Authoritative)

### Worker

```
id: string
name: string
phone: string
skill: enum
location: string
status: active | inactive
created_at: datetime
```

### Job

```
id: string
skill_required: enum
rate: number
min_guarantee: number
date: date
status: open | active | closed
```

### Guarantee Rule

```
id: string
scope: global | job
frequency: daily | weekly
min_amount: number
funding_source: string
```

### Payment

```
id: string
worker_id: string
earned: number
top_up: number
total: number
status: success | failed
transaction_id: string
```

### Ledger Entry (Immutable)

```
id: string
worker_id: string
job_id: string
amount: number
source: earned | topup
timestamp: datetime
```

