## 14. Acceptance Conditions (System-Level)

The system is considered compliant with this spec if:

1. Full lifecycle can be executed end-to-end
2. Income guarantees are enforced deterministically
3. Payments are immutable and traceable
4. Ledger cannot be altered
5. Offline behavior does not corrupt data
6. No hidden state exists

